Installation notes

Sudo yum install sudo yum install python-pip python-devel gcc postgresql-server postgresql-devel postgresql-contrib

sudo service postgresql-setup initdb

sudo service postgresql start

Replace pg_hba.conf (/var/lib/pgsql/data/pg_hba.conf)

